<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Software_architecture&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Collection of <a href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/architecture/definitions.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/architecture/definitions.html" rel="nofollow">software architecture definitions</a> at Software Engineering Institute (SEI), Carnegie Mellon University (CMU)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.eden-study.org/articles/2006/abstraction-classes-sw-design_ieesw.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.eden-study.org/articles/2006/abstraction-classes-sw-design_ieesw.pdf" rel="nofollow">Software architecture vs. software design: The Intension/Locality Hypothesis</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.wwisa.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.wwisa.org/" rel="nofollow">Worldwide Institute of Software Architects (WWISA)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.iasahome.org/iasaweb/appmanager/home/home/" class="external text" title="http://www.iasahome.org/iasaweb/appmanager/home/home/" rel="nofollow">International Association of Software Architects (IASA)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.softwarearchitectureportal.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.softwarearchitectureportal.org/" rel="nofollow">SoftwareArchitecturePortal.org</a> — website of IFIP Working Group 2.10 on Software Architecture</li>
<li><a href="http://www.softwarearchitectures.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.softwarearchitectures.com/" rel="nofollow">SoftwareArchitectures.com</a> — independent resource of information on the discipline</li>
<li><a href="http://www.architecturejournal.net/" class="external text" title="http://www.architecturejournal.net/" rel="nofollow">Microsoft Architecture Journal</a></li>
