<li><a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~fielding/pubs/dissertation/software_arch.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~fielding/pubs/dissertation/software_arch.htm" rel="nofollow">Software Architecture</a>, chapter 1 of <a href="/wiki/Roy_Fielding" title="Roy Fielding">Roy Fielding</a>'s REST dissertation</li>
<li><a href="http://diaspec.bordeaux.inria.fr/" class="external text" title="http://diaspec.bordeaux.inria.fr/" rel="nofollow">DiaSpec</a>, an approach and tool to generate a distributed framework from a software architecture</li>
<li><a href="http://www.methodsandtools.com/archive/archive.php?id=85" class="external text" title="http://www.methodsandtools.com/archive/archive.php?id=85" rel="nofollow">When Good Architecture Goes Bad</a></li>
</ul>
